{"calories":"700","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"The way to our hearts on Valentine’s Day? An all-red dish of red wine risotto combined with thyme-roasted beets, of course. This streamlined dish lets you add all the broth at once so you can skip the elbow grease of constantly stirring your rice—more time to enjoy this dinner of rich, creamy Italian risotto seasoned with pecorino and shaved Parmesan. If this isn’t love, we don’t know what is.","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"c3d0abbf8e","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9536/Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0259_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9537/Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0257_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9537/menu_small_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0257_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/hero_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/menu_small_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/small_square_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/medium_square_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9535/recipe_profile_page_Red_Wine_Risotto_with__Beets_0256_1.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Red Wine Risotto with Thyme-Roasted Beets","novice_time":"","portion_count":2,"prep_time":"35-45","pro_time":"","product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"red-wine-risotto-with-thyme-roasted-beets","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/5962/recipe_card20160129-3-94cbwz.pdf","recipe_id":1263,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Risotto with Beets","subtitle":"with Thyme-Roasted Beets","title":"Red Wine Risotto","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"Be sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did! \r\n\r\nTo remove the thyme leaves, pinch the stem near the top with the fingers of one hand. Swipe down the length of the stem with the fingers of the other hand from top to bottom. The leaves should break off where they meet the stem.\r\n\r\nBe sure to stir the risotto occasionally to prevent it from sticking to the pot.\r\n","equipment":["baking sheet","2 8\" medium pots, 1 with lid"],"id":1263,"ingredients":["shallot","fresh thyme","red beets","yellow beets","vegetable stock","unsalted butter","Arborio rice","red wine","grated pecorino cheese","shaved Parmesan cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"shallot","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/130/medium_square_SHALLOT_copy.jpg"},{"name":"fresh thyme","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1294/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"red beets","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/645/medium_square_veg-beets-red.jpg"},{"name":"yellow beets","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/584/medium_square_beet-test.jpg"},{"name":"vegetable stock","quantity":"32.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/908/medium_square_medium_square_medium_square_beef-broth.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"Arborio rice","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/322/medium_square_rice-arborio.jpg"},{"name":"red wine","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/209/medium_square_RED_COOKING_WINE.jpg"},{"name":"grated pecorino cheese","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/539/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"shaved Parmesan cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/112/medium_square_dairy-cheese-shredded2.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":[],"pantry_items_full":[],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9166/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients_02.jpg","description":"Preheat oven to 425[degrees]F. Peel \u003cb\u003eshallot\u003c/b\u003e and mince. Strip \u003cb\u003ethyme\u003c/b\u003e leaves, discarding stems (see Recipe Tip). Peel \u003cb\u003ebeets\u003c/b\u003e, quarter, and cut into .125-inch slices."},{"title":"Roast Beets","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9167/recipe_card_size_2._Roast_Beets.jpg","description":"On a baking sheet, toss \u003cb\u003ebeets\u003c/b\u003e with \u003cb\u003e.5 of thyme\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003e.5 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/b\u003e, and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e. Arrange in a single layer, transfer to oven, and roast until tender, 15-20 minutes."},{"title":"Sauté Shallot","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9168/recipe_card_size_3._Saute_Shallot.jpg","description":"While beets roast, add \u003cb\u003e3 cups vegetable broth\u003c/b\u003e to a medium pot over medium-high heat and bring to a simmer, then reduce heat to low and cover to keep warm. Heat \u003cb\u003ebutter\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003e.5 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e in a separate medium pot over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cb\u003eshallot\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003eremaining thyme\u003c/b\u003e and sauté, stirring, until softening, about 5 minutes. Use remaining vegetable broth in another recipe as desired."},{"title":"Cook Risotto","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9169/recipe_card_size_4._Cook_Risotto.jpg","description":"Add \u003cb\u003erice\u003c/b\u003e to pot with shallot over medium-high heat and cook, stirring, until toasted, 2-3 minutes. Stir in \u003cb\u003ered wine\u003c/b\u003e and cook until mostly absorbed, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cb\u003ewarm vegetable broth\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003e.5 teaspoon kosher salt\u003c/b\u003e. Increase heat to high and bring to a boil, then reduce heat to medium high and simmer, stirring occasionally, until liquid is absorbed and rice is tender, about 15 minutes. Remove pot from heat."},{"title":"Season Risotto","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9170/recipe_card_size_5._Season_Risotto_1.jpg","description":"Add \u003cb\u003epecorino\u003c/b\u003e to pot with risotto and stir to combine. Stir in \u003cb\u003eroasted beets\u003c/b\u003e. Taste and add more \u003cb\u003esalt\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e as needed."},{"title":"Plate Risotto","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/9171/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Risotto.jpg","description":"Garnish \u003cb\u003erisotto\u003c/b\u003e with \u003cb\u003eParmesan\u003c/b\u003e. Enjoy your masterpiece."}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"No gluten ingredients*","slug":"no-gluten","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}